metadata.name: Valentine's Day
metadata.description:
'I love thee,
With a love that shall not die
Till the sun grows cold
And the stars grow old.'

This painting was made as a present for my colleague and co-author Rossy. Starting my OC Katalina and her husband (my friend's character) Maximilian spending their precious moments together.

Both characters belong to The Inexplicit project, a series of RP stories written since 2010.
